"Most of the time the default implementation of methods or attributes in "
"build system base classes is what a packager needs, and just a very few "
"entities need to be overwritten. Typically we just need to override methods "
"like ``configure_args``:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../packaging_guide.rst:3737
